Package ohos.security.asset

Class AssetResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.security.asset.AssetResult

  • public class AssetResult
extends Object
    Provides the result of storing key asset data.

    The result consists of the result code, result details, and the number of data records in the returned result. Meanings of the three variables may vary depending on the method in which they are used.

    Since:
    1
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.security.asset

    • Method Detail

      • getResultCode

        public int getResultCode​()
        Obtains the result code returned after an operation is performed.
        Returns:
        resultCode.
          The result code can be any of the following:
        • AssetOperator#SUCCESS
        • AssetOperator#ERROR_CODE_INVALID_ARGUMENT
        • AssetOperator#ERROR_CODE_PERMISSION_DENIED
        • AssetOperator#ERROR_CODE_UNINITIALIZED
        • AssetOperator#ERROR_CODE_DATABASE_ERROR
        • AssetOperator#ERROR_CODE_UNSECURED_ENVIRONMENT
        • AssetOperator#ERROR_CODE_SYSTEM_ERROR
        Since:
        1

      • getResultInfo

        public List<String> getResultInfo​()
        Obtains the result details returned after an operation is performed.
        Returns:
        resultInfo.

        For example, the index of asset data is returned in the result of the operation to encrypt and store asset data.

        Since:
        1
